@IndigoLabs.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:7093

### Swagger JSON should be available without authentication
GET {{IndigoLabs.Api_HostAddress}}/swagger/v1/swagger.json
Accept: application/json

### Cache status should return 401 without authentication
GET {{IndigoLabs.Api_HostAddress}}/api/measurements/cache
Accept: application/json

### Cache status should return 401 with wrong credentials
GET {{IndigoLabs.Api_HostAddress}}/api/measurements/cache
Authorization: Basic aW5kaWdvOndyb25n
Accept: application/json

### Missing city should return 404
GET {{IndigoLabs.Api_HostAddress}}/api/cities/Atlantis
Authorization: Basic aW5kaWdvOmxhYnM=
Accept: application/json

### During startup warmup or recalculation, data endpoints can return 503
# Run this immediately after app startup or while a recalculation is already running.
GET {{IndigoLabs.Api_HostAddress}}/api/cities/Paris
Authorization: Basic aW5kaWdvOmxhYnM=
Accept: application/json
